div.div: In this era, people are always reincarnation, but I Lin Fei, depends on being immortal. I have lived for hundreds of million years, just to find my beloved ones that I lost for a million years!!

Cheon Joong Myung, the third son of the CEO of the fifth wealthiest corporation, Ji Gyoung Group. And his assistant working under him, Seong Chang Ook. While Seong Chang Ook tried to kill Cheon Joong Myung and cover it up as an accident, Seong Chang Ook was accidentally electrocuted along with his boss. Thats when they find themselves trapped in each others bodies You want me to become a playboy Conglomerate the world has never seen before? Ill be opening the doors to hell if I do this. This is the start of the endless march of Cheon Joong Myung, the Lord of Money. (Source: Kakao, translated)
